  25,67,"E …ìen taw…ìe si …ìe okkude jawle ma…ì…ìe …óen okkugol ngol …óe ngol hewtintaa…ìe e funsitugol, …ìe …ìittintaa kadi e okkugol …óe ngol on mo nafkugol …óum fawii …ìe immorde e wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe maa…óum tanaa majji, nafkugol ma…ì…ìe ngol laatoo hakkunde funsitugol ngol e …ìittinngol ngol feccaa…óum ka hakkunde."
  25,68,"E …ìen …ìe rewataa wonndude e Alla O Senike rewetee…óo goo, …ìe warataa wonkii ki Alla harmini warugol si wanaa kon ko Alla du≈ãini …óum immorde e wartagol waru…óo maa…óum yartodin…óo maa…óum jeenoowo sa≈ãii…óo, hara …ìe jinataa, kala wa…óu…óo …óii bakkatuuji maw…ói …óoo, o hawroyay √ëalnde Darngal e Lepte ko o wa…ó…óitii kon immorde e bakkaatu."
